snippet.title: Haloween Launch Trailer | Halo Infinite
snippet.description:
Get ready for spooky vibes as Spartanstein rises! 

Operation: Haloween is live until Nov. 5 with the new Survive the Undead playlist in Halo Infinite. Dive into three chilling maps created by the Forge Falcons: Night of the Undead, Countdown of the Dead, and Installation of the Dead.

Celebrate Haloween with a free Operation Pass featuring 20 tiers and the Spartanstein armor set, plus premium options for even more treats! 

#halo #haloinfinite #halloween
